          <p>More things are claims than you might assume. If a claim means something that could be true or could be false, then that means anything that could be true or false, is a claim. Good strategies, bad strategies, good plans, bad plans, good predictions, bad predictions, good decisions, bad decisions, good ethics, bad ethics, assumed problems, assumed solutions, can all be treated as claims.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
